    "MissionGiver": "Citizens for Prosperity",
    "Title": "Deliver Good Cheer",
    "Description": "Hey, \n\nEvery once and awhile, Citizens for Prosperity likes to surprise members stationed at our outposts with a little gift to keep morale high. We\u2019ve got the next box ready to go from <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>, but need someone to make the delivery for us. Any interest in spreading some good cheer?\n\nAlso, to make your life easier, I'd make sure you have a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with you. \n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hey, \n\nEvery once and awhile, Citizens for Prosperity likes to surprise members stationed at our outposts with a little gift to keep morale high. We\u2019ve got the next box ready to go from <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> to <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>, but need someone to make the delivery for us. Any interest in spreading some good cheer?\n\nAlso, to make your life easier, I'd make sure you have a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with you. \n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
